Author: boo_snug
Text: That’s me and baking. I love to bake but I never eat it. I just bring it to my coworkers for them to have.

Author: dragaynite
Text: Yes!!! I found that if I actually take the time to prepare food, the cravings pass while I’m waiting and I’m not even hungry anymore by the time it’s ready. But if I have easily accessible snacks, I’ll consume so much more than I intended >:(
